column2: Johnny Depp is innocent.
column26: Bring Johnny Depp back as Captain Jack Sparrow
column33: Bring Johnny Depp back as Captain Jack Sparrow
column34:
Johnny Depp lost his role as Captain Jack Sparrow in Pirates of the Caribbean due to FALSE Domestic Violence claims by his Ex Wife Amber Heard.

Johnny Depp ‘s Character Captain Jack Sparrow was loved by so many people around the world. This Character became a real life hero to so many. This Character brought so much joy to ill children around the world too. Johnny visited so many childrens hospitals dressed as Captain Jack Sparrow to cheer very sick children up in their darkest times. He didn’t do this for himself or money, he did this for these sick children and that’s now been cruelly taken away from not only him but the world too.

Johnny Depp has a heart of pure Gold. Disney were very wrong in letting Johnny go as Captain Jack Sparrow just because of Amber Heard’s Allegations. That’s all they was. Allegations.

What happened to INNOCENT UNTIL PROVEN GUILTY??

These last two weeks we have seen the truth coming out in the trial of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. It is clear for the world to see that Johnny Depp was in fact the Victim of Domestic Violence not the Perpetrator. Due to this, I have set up this Petition in the hope to show DISNEY that they have made a HUGE mistake and to bring Johnny Depp back to Pirates of the Caribbean to resume his role as Captain Jack Sparrow.

please sign the petition and share with everyone. Let’s all Show Disney that there is only one Johnny Depp and only one Captain Jack Sparrow. Let’s show Disney that the whole entire world are behind Johnny Depp and support him 100%. 


WE STAND BY JOHHNY DEPP AKA CAPTAIN JACK SPARROW ❤️

DISNEY PLEASE DO THE RIGHT THING AND BRING HIM BACK. SUPPORT HIM AS HE SUPPORTED YOU.

column2: I, Stephanie Brown, am signing because I really, really want to see my absolute favorite actor, Johnny Depp as the one and only Captain Jack Sparrow in Pirates of the Caribbean 6! Without him, the sixth movie will not succeed at the Disney box office like the five-film series did before he lost his iconic job, all because of the op-ed Washington Post and false allegations conducted by his abusive ex-wife! Anyway, what's a Pirates movie without Johnny Depp? Nothing but a fail-to-sail out on the open sea! So, if you could just please be so kind as to return one of my favorite icons to the Disney Pirates of the Caribbean movie series that would be fantastic!

Johnny Depp lost his role as Captain Jack Sparrow in Pirates of the Caribbean due to FALSE Domestic Violence claims by his Ex Wife Amber Heard.

Johnny Depp ‘s Character Captain Jack Sparrow was loved by so many people around the world. This Character became a real life hero to so many. This Character brought so much joy to ill children around the world too. Johnny visited so many childrens hospitals dressed as Captain Jack Sparrow to cheer very sick children up in their darkest times. He didn’t do this for himself or money, he did this for these sick children and that’s now been cruelly taken away from not only him but the world too.

Johnny Depp has a heart of pure Gold. Disney were very wrong in letting Johnny go as Captain Jack Sparrow just because of Amber Heard’s Allegations. That’s all they was. Allegations.

What happened to INNOCENT UNTIL PROVEN GUILTY??

These last two weeks we have seen the truth coming out in the trial of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. It is clear for the world to see that Johnny Depp was in fact the Victim of Domestic Violence not the Perpetrator. Due to this, I have set up this Petition in the hope to show DISNEY that they have made a HUGE mistake and to bring Johnny Depp back to Pirates of the Caribbean to resume his role as Captain Jack Sparrow.

please sign the petition and share with everyone. Let’s all Show Disney that there is only one Johnny Depp and only one Captain Jack Sparrow. Let’s show Disney that the whole entire world are behind Johnny Depp and support him 100%. 


WE STAND BY JOHHNY DEPP AKA CAPTAIN JACK SPARROW ❤️

DISNEY PLEASE DO THE RIGHT THING AND BRING HIM BACK. SUPPORT HIM AS HE SUPPORTED YOU.

column34:
Johnny Depp lost his role as Captain Jack Sparrow in Pirates of the Caribbean due to FALSE Domestic Violence claims by his Ex Wife Amber Heard.

Johnny Depp ‘s Character Captain Jack Sparrow was loved by so many people around the world. This Character became a real life hero to so many. This Character brought so much joy to ill children around the world too. Johnny visited so many childrens hospitals dressed as Captain Jack Sparrow to cheer very sick children up in their darkest times. He didn’t do this for himself or money, he did this for these sick children and that’s now been cruelly taken away from not only him but the world too.

Johnny Depp has a heart of pure Gold. Disney were very wrong in letting Johnny go as Captain Jack Sparrow just because of Amber Heard’s Allegations. That’s all they was. Allegations.

What happened to INNOCENT UNTIL PROVEN GUILTY??

These last two weeks we have seen the truth coming out in the trial of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. It is clear for the world to see that Johnny Depp was in fact the Victim of Domestic Violence not the Perpetrator. Due to this, I have set up this Petition in the hope to show DISNEY that they have made a HUGE mistake and to bring Johnny Depp back to Pirates of the Caribbean to resume his role as Captain Jack Sparrow.

please sign the petition and share with everyone. Let’s all Show Disney that there is only one Johnny Depp and only one Captain Jack Sparrow. Let’s show Disney that the whole entire world are behind Johnny Depp and support him 100%. 


WE STAND BY JOHHNY DEPP AKA CAPTAIN JACK SPARROW ❤️

DISNEY PLEASE DO THE RIGHT THING AND BRING HIM BACK. SUPPORT HIM AS HE SUPPORTED YOU.

column34:
Johnny Depp lost his role as Captain Jack Sparrow in Pirates of the Caribbean due to FALSE Domestic Violence claims by his Ex Wife Amber Heard.

Johnny Depp ‘s Character Captain Jack Sparrow was loved by so many people around the world. This Character became a real life hero to so many. This Character brought so much joy to ill children around the world too. Johnny visited so many childrens hospitals dressed as Captain Jack Sparrow to cheer very sick children up in their darkest times. He didn’t do this for himself or money, he did this for these sick children and that’s now been cruelly taken away from not only him but the world too.

Johnny Depp has a heart of pure Gold. Disney were very wrong in letting Johnny go as Captain Jack Sparrow just because of Amber Heard’s Allegations. That’s all they was. Allegations.

What happened to INNOCENT UNTIL PROVEN GUILTY??

These last two weeks we have seen the truth coming out in the trial of Johnny Depp and Amber Heard. It is clear for the world to see that Johnny Depp was in fact the Victim of Domestic Violence not the Perpetrator. Due to this, I have set up this Petition in the hope to show DISNEY that they have made a HUGE mistake and to bring Johnny Depp back to Pirates of the Caribbean to resume his role as Captain Jack Sparrow.

please sign the petition and share with everyone. Let’s all Show Disney that there is only one Johnny Depp and only one Captain Jack Sparrow. Let’s show Disney that the whole entire world are behind Johnny Depp and support him 100%. 


WE STAND BY JOHHNY DEPP AKA CAPTAIN JACK SPARROW ❤️

DISNEY PLEASE DO THE RIGHT THING AND BRING HIM BACK. SUPPORT HIM AS HE SUPPORTED YOU.
